---
import { MessageCircle, ArrowRight } from '@lucide/astro';
import Ornament from '../Ornament.astro';
---
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-primary relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-islamic-pattern opacity-15"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1/2 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/10 to-transparent -z-10"></div>
  
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10">
    <div class="animate-on-scroll inline-flex justify-center items-center mb-6">
      <span class="font-arabic text-3xl md:text-4xl text-accent font-semibold leading-relaxed">رَبَّنَا آتِنَا فِي الدُّنْيَا حَسَنَةً وَفِي الْآخِرَةِ حَسَنَةً</span>
    </div>
    
    <h2 class="animate-on-scroll text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-4">Amankan Masa Depan Anda Hari Ini.</h2>
    <Ornament type="divider" class="mb-6 animate-on-scroll" />
    
    <p class="animate-on-scroll text-base md:text-xl text-white/90 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">Bergabunglah dengan komunitas pemuda Muslim penggerak perubahan yang bersiap memimpin di era digital. Kuota beasiswa 2026 sangat terbatas.</p>
    
    <div class="animate-on-scroll flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
      <a href="https://wa.me/6285183003060" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-wrap text-sm sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-accent hover:text-accent-light font-bold gap-2 group transition-colors px-4">
        <MessageCircle class="w-5 h-5 shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" />
        <span>
          <span class="hidden sm:inline">Hubungi </span>WhatsApp <span class="hidden sm:inline">Pendaftaran</span>: +62 851 8300 3060
        </span>
        <ArrowRight class="w-5 h-5 shrink-0 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" />
      </a>
      <p class="text-xs text-white/70 mt-3">Pendaftaran segera ditutup. Konsultasi gratis tanpa dipungut biaya.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
